Class Discord4J.Discord4JLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.slf4j.helpers.MarkerIgnoringBase
      • sx.blah.discord.Discord4J.Discord4JLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.slf4j.Logger
    Enclosing class:
    Discord4J

    public static class Discord4J.Discord4JLogger
extends org.slf4j.helpers.MarkerIgnoringBase
    This is a logger implementation used by Discord4J if no valid SLF4J implementation is found.

        public void setLevel(Discord4J.Discord4JLogger.Level level)
        Sets the level for this logger. Messages will only be logged if the message level >= the current level.
        Parameters:
        level - The level for the logger.
